data.description: Well maintained Tri-Level home on quiet cul-de-sac minutes from New Albany, Easton & Polaris. This lovely home features cathedral ceilings throughout, 4 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, a 2 car att. gar. Large open living room, formal dining room, updated kitchen with eating space, sliding doors lead to updated upper deck (balcony). Level 3 large master bedroom suite with sitting room/office/den and half bth. full bath features soaking tub. LL features large fam room with wb fplc with a brick surround and a walkout patio. All appliances remain including washer and dryer. Loads of upgrades. Must see 👀
